metadata.name: Résonance de Couple
metadata.description:
This artwork is about how human beings are receptive beings and how much they transmit when they are with others, our thoughts, pain, happiness, memories, pleasures, all of this can be shared and ends up being absorbed by those we love. Over time, all this is manifested in different ways in the other person, clothing, way of speaking, quirks. A resonant couple.

Another work inspired by Gothic and Victorianism.
Résonance de Couple

Created with Photoshop/Blender/Collage and Painting Techniques.

 2200 x 2700 - PNG - 13.8MB
